					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10876467#post-4201960</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10876467/scp-4970#post-4201960</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 30 Mar 2019 12:31:21 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Mortos</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1705184</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>There's a lot I like about this one but the 2 main things that I really enjoyed is the idea of a universe repair man, for people who break their universe, and just how weirdly sinister it is that the the answer to what love is was restricted to O5 level clearance. I think the formatting of the table at the end could use a bit of altering just so the first panel isn't so squashed, though.</p> <p>Either way, +1.</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Some&nbsp;minor&nbsp;issues</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>Note: I pointed these out on IRC but I don't know if you saw them; if you did you can disregard this.</p> <blockquote> <p>&quot;SCP-4970-2: The original owner must have? That's not practical, on account of them being dead. &quot;</p> </blockquote> <p>You still have the phone guy refering to the old owner as being dead here, which I think was in an older verison when the foundation guy told him that? But that isnt the case anymore</p> <blockquote> <p>&quot;Date: 24.02.2019&quot;</p> </blockquote> <p>You've got a note saying 7 previous conversations have taken place between these 2, but the date is still only 1 day later, which is fine, but that's a pretty busy day.</p> <blockquote> <p>&quot;Dr. Collins: We have some anomalous that can be considered extra-dimensional.&quot;</p> </blockquote> <p>anomalous -&gt; anomalies?</p> </div> </div> </div> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10876467#post-4201935</guid>
				<title>Author Post</title>
